{"tid":660599,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"不要劇透，死侍請求粉絲保持沉默","createTime":"2018-05-10T22:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T02:12:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"68f2e88de7f96e77b1ec34237c74525713a4227c","tid":660599,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T22:54:24.000Z","msg":"&quot;多嘴的傭兵&rdquo;請求粉絲們不要劇透《死侍2（Deadpool 2）》。日前，動作喜劇電影《死侍2》主演瑞安・雷諾茲（Ryan Reynolds）在個人移動社交平台上分享了一封搞笑的信，請求粉絲對劇情保持沉默，不要劇透。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，導演喬・羅素（Joe Russo）和安東尼・羅素（Anthony Russo）曾分享了他們致粉絲的公開信，請求粉絲不要劇透《復仇者聯盟3：無限戰爭（Avengers：Infinity War）》。<br />\n<br />\n雷諾茲公開的信件以&ldquo;整個宇宙中最偉大的粉絲&rdquo;為開頭，超過羅素兄弟以&ldquo;世界上最偉大的粉絲&rdquo;的開頭。接著這封信寫道：&ldquo;只有少數人知道《死侍2》的真實情節，這其中並不包括瑞安・雷諾茲。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/065337_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F065337_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b11b1c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/065345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F065345_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6b0ba960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f5042e69bced3df9e11f661d42b48578458d0d5","tid":660599,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"隻狗手係咩意思"},{"pid":"70f2b342fc3e436688e61543467ac52ad09be9d5","tid":660599,"uid":30006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f5042e69bced3df9e11f661d42b48578458d0d5","tid":660599,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"隻狗手係咩意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:02:52.000Z","msg":"Dc"},{"pid":"4747debc483e2f29d062073d42ce68be81bdb8f9","tid":660599,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"70f2b342f